    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve finally found the mysterious <strong>Dang Darn Island</strong>! Now the only thing standing between you and the legendary <strong>Gold Idol</strong> is an ancient temple filled with slithering snakes, pointy spikes, flamethrowers, poison darts, and a grumpy volcano who just might lose his cool at any moment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piece of cake, right?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Smash Pots!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave a trail of ceramic mayhem in your wake as you search for useful items to help you on your quest. Be careful, though! Some of those innocent looking containers will give you more than you bargained for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/b3b9562986530b372217e61e7b9e9c5f.poster.avif?t=1759324422\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/b3b9562986530b372217e61e7b9e9c5f.webm?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/b3b9562986530b372217e61e7b9e9c5f.mp4?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dodge Traps!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are more than a few ways to get caught off guard in this labyrinth of doom. Watch your step and try not to get stabbed, poisoned, sliced, or fried.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/05f14f3662791114d52c8166d5e4f9d7.poster.avif?t=1759324422\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/05f14f3662791114d52c8166d5e4f9d7.webm?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/05f14f3662791114d52c8166d5e4f9d7.mp4?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Appease The Volcano!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paul Cano, the talking volcano that runs this island, has a bit of a temper. Better stay on his good side, or things will heat up quickly. An offering or two…or three…might help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/d5de07938604d6f3f7fa7ca40aedabc0.poster.avif?t=1759324422\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/d5de07938604d6f3f7fa7ca40aedabc0.webm?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/d5de07938604d6f3f7fa7ca40aedabc0.mp4?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Search For Clues!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you can put the pieces together and crack the code? Use everything at your disposal to open the path to fortune and glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/d90a7ecf846bc6485adaa01b1f7ce1b4.poster.avif?t=1759324422\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/d90a7ecf846bc6485adaa01b1f7ce1b4.webm?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/d90a7ecf846bc6485adaa01b1f7ce1b4.mp4?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect Stickers!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade stickers can give you an edge in all kinds of situations. Level up to collect more and customize your kit on every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/faea8bcaf9955300bdc6d4456b86d6ec.poster.avif?t=1759324422\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/faea8bcaf9955300bdc6d4456b86d6ec.webm?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/faea8bcaf9955300bdc6d4456b86d6ec.mp4?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Invite Your Pals!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s rough out there for a lonely adventurer. Call up some friends and share the pain…er…uh…fun with online or local split screen multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/cb7552a68dc01f2e69aead7f5e45d754.poster.avif?t=1759324422\" width=616 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/cb7552a68dc01f2e69aead7f5e45d754.webm?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802370/extras/cb7552a68dc01f2e69aead7f5e45d754.mp4?t=1759324422\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
